      "reason": "Directly addresses clinical health-aware reasoning and reliability in text generation, relevant to medical QA trustworthiness.",
      "doi": "10.48550/arXiv.2210.04191",
      "url": "https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/ad62d710f1854daf372680263f50a4e135e309f2",
