      "reason": "The candidate applies LLMs to fitness coaching, not medical question answering, so it shares the method (LLM) but differs in domain and object, making it only tangentially relevant.",
      "doi": null,
      "url": "https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/b52e042acfd6de6cbc262b18dea6a35665b0e055",
