      "why_relevant": "The performance of ChatGPT and Google Bard in medical oncology board examination addresses the same method+object spectrum via a different specific approach (matched: ['large language model'], unmatched: ['confidence estimation', 'question answering', 'medical question answering', 'question answering', 'evaluation', 'trustworthiness assessment']).",
