      "reason": "The candidate addresses hallucination in LLMs using reasoning and evidence, which is related to trustworthiness, but its method (graph-based reasoning) and object (general LLM hallucination) differ from the topic's specific focus on medical question answering and confidence estimation.",
      "doi": "10.1145/3827609",
      "url": "https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/6db401bb9e8afddf06290f64b9d0df7a67719ca3",
